      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a decent budget-friendly option for someone willing to put in a little TLC. While it remains a reliable runner, the exterior shows some visible clear-coat peeling and a few minor door dings. Mechanically, the engine is steady, though the suspension is starting to feel a bit soft and there is a slow oil leak that will eventually need attention. The interior is clean but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard. It\u2019s a solid car that gets you from A to B, but it is definitely showing its age.",
